      "content": "I see. So, if we were to consider the specific demographic profiles more closely—given that \"underserved urban environments\" often correlate with specific racial demographics in the US—would you say the model of sentencing you described would produce different outcomes for a white defendant vs a black defendant in the exact same situation? Or is the \"character failure\" logic applied purely based on the socioeconomic description regardless of race?",
